## 🚀 Quick Start

### Installation

```python
# Add COMMON directory to your Python path
import sys
sys.path.insert(0, '/path/to/COMMON')

# Import everything
from COMMON import *

# Or import specific modules
from COMMON.config import Config, PathConfig
from COMMON.io_utils import read_fixed_width_file
from COMMON.date_utils import get_reporting_dates
```

