## 🧪 Testing

Create `test_common.py`:

```python
from COMMON import *
import unittest

class TestSASFunctions(unittest.TestCase):
    def test_left(self):
        self.assertEqual(left('  hello'), 'hello')
    
    def test_upcase(self):
        self.assertEqual(upcase('hello'), 'HELLO')
    
    def test_mdy(self):
        date = mdy(10, 23, 2025)
        self.assertEqual(date.year, 2025)

if __name__ == '__main__':
    unittest.main()
```

